Author: yeasomerandosaidso
Text: I want to add that what pisses me off most is that I've never been underweight. Closest I've gotten is 8lbs away. And despite all the stupid crap I've put myself through, I've never been there.  I've wanted to die, and that's not happened either. Half hoped to be one of those anorexic runners who gets a heart attack mid-run. Nope. Still fat, still alive. What the actual fuck.
